<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="images/favicon.ico">
    <title>Amy Zinger's NFT Mint</title>
    <meta name="author" content="Amy Zinger">
    <meta name="description" content="A personal NFT mint for artist Amy Zinger.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sedan+SC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
   <%- include('navigation') %>

    <!-- Header (Banner Area) -->
    <header class="banner">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-1">Amy Zinger</h1>
            <p class="display-14">Creative Director | Serial Tinkerer | Gentlewoman Adventurer</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main>
            <!-- Featured -->

            <section class="content-section" id="featured">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 class="section-title">Featured Work</h2>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <%- include('projectCard', {image: featuredProject.img_url, name: featuredProject.project_name, ident: featuredProject.id}); %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean aliquet ipsum sit amet purus tristique volutpat. Aliquam feugiat nulla vel cursus ultricies. Donec tincidunt lacinia eleifend. Ut hendrerit vel metus non commodo. Fusce at ante a turpis imperdiet varius. Etiam bibendum nulla mauris, et euismod dolor venenatis sed. Phasellus eleifend ipsum vel pulvinar fermentum. Phasellus id vehicula tortor, nec aliquam dolor. Morbi maximus aliquet mi, sit amet vehicula odio ornare at. Duis euismod ac purus ac tincidunt.</p>
                            <a href="/project"><button class="btn btn-primary mt-3">View Project</button></a><br>
                            <a href="/projects"><button class="btn btn-secondary mt-3">Explore More Work</button></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        <section class="content-section section2" id="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">About Amy</h2>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                        <img src="images/AmyZinger.jpg" alt="Description of image 2" class="img-fluid rounded">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                        <div>
                            Amy Zinger believes everyone and everything has a story to tell. As a creative director and 
                            writer, she's told stories for some of the world's most well-known brands, and as a soprano, she's
                            brought some of opera's most beloved characters to life&mdash;including the iconic Queen of 
                            the Night. Her other interests include coding (badly), photography (passably), cooking (well), 
                            and playing chess (also badly). Amy lives in Dallas, Texas, with her husband, daughter, and 
                            three ridiculous dogs. She is never bored.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Form Section -->
        <section class="content-section" id="contact">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Questions or comments?</h2>
                <p>We'd love to hear from you. Please fill out the form and we'll be in touch as soon as possible.</p>
                <div class="contact-form">
                    <form id="contact-form" novalidate>
                        <div class="row mb-4">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="contact-first">First Name</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contact-first" placeholder="Jane" required>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your first name.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="contact-last">Last Name</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contact-last" placeholder="Doe" required>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your last name.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-4">
                            <label for="contact-email-addr">Email address</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="contact-email-addr" placeholder="jane.doe@example.com" required>
                            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a valid email address.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group mb-4">
                            <label for="contact-question">Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="contact-question" rows="5" placeholder="Enter your message" required></textarea>
                            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your message.</div>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" id="send-contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Submit</button>
                        <div id="contact-button-response" class="mt-3"></div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <div class-"container-fluid">
        <!-- Footer -->
        <%- include('footer') %>
</div>

    <!-- <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script> -->
    <script type="module" src="./js/contact.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
